 They got engaged in December 2021 and shared their story of divorce and re-finding love on their podcast. You can catch up with that here. Sharing the photos on their Instagram page, they wrote, “#MeetTheSnatchas – Part 2: The King & His Queen | @soulsnatcha & @NikkiLaoye – Official pictures coming soon: Best Friends of Life… now For Life. God gave us a mind-blowing second chance, he gave us beauty for ashes…” We can’t wait to see more pictures from their beautiful wedding. Here are two pictures we are currently crushing on of the couple! <img loading="lazy" class=" wp-image-1538970 aligncenter" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/276010787_718857965963056_538161523577551303_n-300x300.jpg?resize=942%2C942&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="942" height="942" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/276010787_718857965963056_538161523577551303_n-300x300.jpg?resize=942%2C942&#038;ssl=1 300w, https://www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/276010787_718857965963056_538161523577551303_n-600x599.jpg 600w, https://www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/276010787_718857965963056_538161523577551303_n-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/276010787_718857965963056_538161523577551303_n-768x767.jpg 768w, https://www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/276010787_718857965963056_538161523577551303_n-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/276010787_718857965963056_538161523577551303_n-80x80.jpg 80w, https://www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/276010787_718857965963056_538161523577551303_n.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 942px) 100vw, 942px" data-recalc-dims="1"> <img loading="lazy" class=" wp-image-1538971 aligncenter" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/276044501_546821773318654_3545208099525475539_n-300x300.jpg?resize=940%2C940&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="940" height="940" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/ww